PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F163A1779977469
OL,1,Wj5hw1~{4k7juhw1{$             G3/3
OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Fri 12 Jun to Fri 26 Jun
OL,6,FStill fairly changeable or unsettled
OL,7,Fat first, with Atlantic frontal
OL,8,Fsystems bringing showers or longer
OL,9,Fspells of rain particularly into the
OL,10,Fnorth and west at times. Otherwise
OL,11,Fhigh pressure may become more dominant
OL,12,Fwith weather conditions becoming drier
OL,13,Fand more settled, although some
OL,14,Fshowery interludes are still possible.
OL,15,FTemperatures are expected to be near
OL,16,Fnormal at first, but probably rising
OL,17,Fabove average as we head further into
OL,18,FJune.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
